<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>指令陷阱 on cmdragon's Blog</title><link>https://blog.cmdragon.cn/tags/%E6%8C%87%E4%BB%A4%E9%99%B7%E9%98%B1/</link><description>Recent content in 指令陷阱 on cmdragon's Blog</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh-cn</language><lastBuildDate>Tue, 19 May 2026 12:00:00 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://blog.cmdragon.cn/tags/%E6%8C%87%E4%BB%A4%E9%99%B7%E9%98%B1/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>把自定义指令贴到组件上，为啥有时候不生效？</title><link>https://blog.cmdragon.cn/posts/e7a9d1f3c5b8e0a2d4f6a8c0e2b4d6f8/</link><pubDate>Tue, 19 May 2026 12:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://blog.cmdragon.cn/posts/e7a9d1f3c5b8e0a2d4f6a8c0e2b4d6f8/</guid><description>自定义指令用在普通HTML元素上没问题，但贴到组件上就可能翻车。单根组件指令会透传到根节点，多根组件直接报警告，而且指令不能像attributes那样用v-bind=&amp;quot;$attrs&amp;quot;手动传递。这篇文章帮你搞明白指令在组件上的那些坑。</description></item></channel></rss>